### CREATE STUDENT
POST http://localhost:5000/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John",
  "course": "IT"
}

### GET ALL STUDENTS
GET http://localhost:5000/students

### GET ONE STUDENT
GET http://localhost:5000/students/0

### UPDATE STUDENT
PUT http://localhost:5000/students/0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "course": "Computer Science"
}

### DELETE STUDENT
DELETE http://localhost:5000/students/0

### REGISTER USER
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "1234"
}

### LOGIN USER
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "1234"
}

